window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Trust is a valuable commodity, and Nico has very little of it to spare.</b></p> <p>Discovering the condition of other dragons in the empire rocked Nico. Now he has to decide how to respond.</p> <p>Is it time to spread his wings and fly, or will Nico double down and learn the power these humans have to teach him?</p> <p>It isn't really trust when both sides are trying to use the other.</p>"; 
